  {
    "type": "hardware-ref",
    "page": "4",
    "id": "hardware-reference",
    "head": {
      "title": {
        "en": "HARDWARE — REFERENCE",
        "zh": "五金件 — 参考"
      }
    },
    "entries": [
      {
        "iconLabel": "[ SHCS icon ]",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Socket head cap screw (SHCS)",
          "zh": "内六角圆柱头螺钉（SHCS）"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Cylindrical head, hex drive. The default fastener for PhysiClaw.ai — used wherever the head can sit above the surface.",
          "zh": "圆柱头，用内六角扳手拧。PhysiClaw.ai 最常用的螺钉——只要螺钉头可以露在表面外，就用它。"
        },
        "ref": {
          "en": "ISO 4762 / DIN 912",
          "zh": "ISO 4762 / DIN 912"
        }
      },
      {
        "iconLabel": "[ BHCS icon ]",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Button head cap screw (BHCS)",
          "zh": "内六角盘头螺钉（BHCS）"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Domed head, hex drive. Used on surfaces where a lower profile matters but a flush head isn't required.",
          "zh": "圆顶头，用内六角扳手拧。用在既想压低高度、又不必和表面齐平的地方。"
        },
        "ref": {
          "en": "ISO 7380-1",
          "zh": "ISO 7380-1"
        }
      },
      {
        "iconLabel": "[ T-nut icon ]",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Extrusion T-nut",
          "zh": "型材 T 型螺母"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Drops into a 2020 / 2040 aluminum extrusion channel and locks under a screw head. Every frame-attached part rides on these.",
          "zh": "放进 2020 / 2040 铝型材的滑槽里，被螺钉头压住卡紧。凡是装到框架上的零件，都靠它固定。"
        }
      },
      {
        "iconLabel": "[ hex nut icon ]",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Hex nut",
          "zh": "六角螺母"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Standard M3 hex nut, paired with a screw to clamp parts together where a T-nut won't fit.",
          "zh": "标准 M3 六角螺母。在装不下 T 型螺母的地方，用它配上螺钉把零件夹紧。"
        },
        "ref": {
          "en": "ISO 4032 / DIN 934",
          "zh": "ISO 4032 / DIN 934"
        }
      },
      {
        "iconLabel": "[ MGN9H icon ]",
        "h3": {
          "en": "MGN9H linear rail + slider",
          "zh": "MGN9H 直线导轨 + 滑块"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "9 mm-wide miniature linear guide. Two rails run the Y axis, two more carry the X beam. Mounting pitch is 16 × 15 mm — don't substitute.",
          "zh": "9 mm 宽的微型直线导轨。Y 轴用两条，另外两条托着 X 横梁。安装孔的间距是 16 × 15 mm——别拿别的型号替换。"
        }
      },
      {
        "iconLabel": "[ GT2 belt + pulley ]",
        "h3": {
          "en": "GT2 belt &amp; pulley",
          "zh": "GT2 同步带与同步带轮"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "2 mm-pitch open-loop belt, clamped at each end to the stylus carriage. The pulleys are 20-tooth; one per stepper, plus smooth idlers.",
          "zh": "齿距 2 mm 的开口同步带，两端分别夹在触控笔滑座上。同步带轮是 20 齿的，每个步进电机配一个，再加上几个光面惰轮。"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "printed-parts",
    "page": "5",
    "id": "printed-parts",
    "head": {
      "title": {
        "en": "3D PRINTED PARTS",
        "zh": "3D 打印件"
      }
    },
    "notesBefore": [
      {
        "h3": {
          "en": "Part printing settings and guidelines",
          "zh": "零件打印设置与说明"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "PhysiClaw's custom parts are printed by Selective Laser Sintering (SLS), not the common FDM. A laser fuses nylon powder in a heated powder bed, so parts come out fully solid, support-free, and strong in every direction. These parts carry side holes and overhangs: with FDM the side holes deform and the overhangs sag. Match the specifications below when sourcing parts.",
          "zh": "PhysiClaw 的定制零件用选择性激光烧结（SLS）打印，而不是常见的 FDM。激光在加热的粉末床里把尼龙粉末烧结成型，做出来的零件完全实心、不用支撑，各个方向都很结实。这些零件带有侧面的孔和悬空结构，用 FDM 打，侧孔会变形、悬空处会塌陷。采购零件时，请对照下面的规格。"
        },
        "classes": "note"
      }
    ],
    "specs": [
      {
        "k": {
          "en": "3D Printing Process",
          "zh": "3D 打印工艺"
        },
        "v": {
